Distributions

  ggplot(aes(x = body_mass_g)) +
  geom_histogram(bins = 10) +
  aes(fill = species) +
  facet_wrap(~species)

penguins %>% 
  
  drop_na() %>% 
  
  ggplot(aes(x = body_mass_g)) +
  geom_histogram(bins = 10) +
  aes(fill = species) +
  facet_grid(sex ~ species)
